at 1293(967– 1550) m elevation in montane rainforest (
<figureCitation box="[638,726,654,680]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="40.[159,269,1195,1218]" captionTargetBox="[170,1417,161,1170]" captionTargetId="figure@40.[151,1436,141,1190]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 10. Distribution maps of Geonoma braunii, G. brenesii, G. brongniartii subsp. brongniartii, and G. brongniartii subsp. pascoensis." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3538382" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3538382/files/figure.png" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
